<item>
            <title>[CXF-1780] float&apos;s and double&apos;s negative infinity is incorrectly marshalled/unmarshalled as positive infinity</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-1780</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Floats with value Float.NEGATIVE_INFINITY or doubles with value Double.NEGATIVE_INFINITY are incorrectly marshalled/unmarshalled as positive infinity.&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12403532">CXF-1780</key>
